creator: Signature Strata
descriptionHtml: This app assists all Owners direct access to Owners Corporations documents, being able to view and pay levy contributions as well as report any common property maintenance issues. Everything that you need about your Owners Corporation, easily accessible on your phone.
descriptionShort: Everything that you need about your Owners Corporation, easily accessible.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Forms
Submit and track forms forms such as pet requests and insurance claims. Receive push notifications whenever there’s an update, and see a full history of all changes. Forms will appear under the “Requests” section when they are available.
Updates
* Levy notices for now show the correct issue date and are ordered so the most recent is at the top of the page
* Improved buttons on the additional profile items so they are the correct theme

Updates
- You can download any file from a CommitteeHub topic. This is useful if viewing items on the online portal from a computer
- Users who register manually are no longer shown as inactive users for the first 24 hours
- Improved buttons on the additional profile items so they are the correct theme

Bug Fix
- Resident app does not show all requests
- Site request names not always showing
- API Documents not Appearing in App but appearing in web portal
- Additional details section not able to be updated on resident app/portal
- Angular framework Learning for both Admin Console and Mobile App
